make_corpse
Discworld living help
make_corpse

Name
.SI 5
make_corpse - Makes a corpse.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
void make_corpse();
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
This makes a corpse with all the right descriptions, and moves the
objects inventory onto the corpse keeping the wielded/worn status of
all the objects.  This also sets up the corpse with the correct race
for bit calculation.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
death, second_life
.EP
